    <note>Shan(1) Xin [21481] Yuan Yueyou, WJ, 20.22b-30a (wife, born Ye, who died in 1185 at age 82). Born Ye's father was a Jianning resident, who moved to the home of his wife, born Yang(2), a Jianning, Pucheng resident, who had moved to Suzhou--almost certainly the family of Yang(2) Bangbi [2021], a Hongnong Yang(2) great great grandson of Yang(2) Yi(3) [7097]. born Yang's sister was also married to a Suzhou resident, Wei(5), which must be Wei(5) Xian's [7092] lineage, both Yang(2) Bangbi and Wei(5) Xian were Wujiang county residents. born Ye was only 30 years old when her husband died. CBD, 4, 2963.</note>
